m/news/tv/one-tree-hill-to-return-for-netflix-sequel-with-original-cast-3789526">Netflix 续集《一树山》回归，原班人马</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Cast-of-‘One-Tree-Hill.-Hilarie-Burton-Bethany-Joy-Lenz-Chad-Michael-Murray-Sophia-Bush-and-James-Lafferty.-CREDIT_-Theo-Wargo_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《一树山》演员表。海拉莉·伯顿、贝瑟尼·乔伊·伦茨、查德·迈克尔·默里、索菲亚·布什和詹姆斯·拉弗蒂。图片来源：Theo Wargo/WireImage" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Cast-of-‘One-Tree-Hill.-Hilarie-Burton-Bethany-Joy-Lenz-Chad-Michael-Murray-Sophia-Bush-and-James-Lafferty.-CREDIT_-Theo-Wargo_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Cast-of-‘One-Tree-Hill.-Hilarie-Burton-Bethany-Joy-Lenz-Chad-Michael-Murray-Sophia-Bush-and-James-Lafferty.-CREDIT_-Theo-Wargo_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Cast-of-‘One-Tree-Hill.-Hilarie-Burton-Bethany-Joy-Lenz-Chad-Michael-Murray-Sophia-Bush-and-James-Lafferty.-CREDIT_-Theo-Wargo_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Cast-of-‘One-Tree-Hill.-Hilarie-Burton-Bethany-Joy-Lenz-Chad-Michael-Murray-Sophia-Bush-and-James-Lafferty.-CREDIT_-Theo-Wargo_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Cast-of-‘One-Tree-Hill.-Hilarie-Burton-Bethany-Joy-Lenz-Chad-Michael-Murray-Sophia-Bush-and-James-Lafferty.-CREDIT_-Theo-Wargo_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Cast-of-‘One-Tree-Hill.-Hilarie-Burton-Bethany-Joy-Lenz-Chad-Michael-Murray-Sophia-Bush-and-James-Lafferty.-CREDIT_-Theo-Wargo_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>青少年剧集<em>《一树山》</em>将于 12 年后携<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>续集回归。</p><p>原剧从 2003 年到 2012 年共播出九季，首先在 WB 播出，然后在 CW 播出。该剧讲述了虚构的北卡罗来纳州树山镇青少年的生活以及他们成年后发生的戏剧性事件。</p><p>据报道，现在该剧的重启工作正在进行中，明星索菲亚·布什、希拉里·伯顿和丹尼尔·阿克斯将重新扮演他们的角色并担任该剧的执行制片人。</p><p>目前还不清楚在原版剧集中扮演同父异母兄弟的搭档查德·迈克尔·默里和詹姆斯·拉弗蒂是否也会回归。默里目前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/lindsay-lohan-and-jamie-lee-curtis-reveal-freaky-friday-sequel-title-3782619">正在即将上映的<em>《怪异星期五》</em>续集<em>《怪异星期五》</em>中再次扮演杰克，</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lindsay-lohan">林赛·罗韩</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jamie-lee-curtis">杰米·李·柯蒂斯</a>一起出演。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.vulture.com/article/one-tree-hill-sequel-netflix.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Vulture</em></a>报道，Netflix 的新剧集将在该剧最后一集 20 年后讲述，并讲述演员们如何抚养自己的青少年。</p><p>在原剧中饰演布鲁克·戴维斯的布什周五（8月30日）在Instagram上宣布了这一消息，并写道：“如果你真的可以回家怎么办？是否有机会与才华横溢的创意人士合作，打造一个让我们所有朋友都能展示才华的空间？拥有我们的历史？夺回我们的地盘？尊重我们的粉丝吗？给我们报名吧。”</p><p>她接着说：“毕竟只有一座树山。而你们——#OTHfam——向我们表明，这不仅仅是一个想法。这确实是一个“一切都更好、一切都安全”的地方。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_UGIjyptXS/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="h